          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level of this stored procedure is medium. It involves multiple operations across different tables and stored procedures, uses transactions for data integrity, and includes error handling mechanisms. The use of multiple input parameters and the integration of several business logic components contribute to its complexity."
